<H2 style=3D"CLEAR: both" class=3Dtitle><A=20
id=3Ddisclaimer></A>Disclaimer</H2></DIV></DIV></DIV>
<P>Many project websites link to this document in their sections on how =
to get=20
help. That's fine, it's the use we intended =E2=80=94 but if you are a =
webmaster=20
creating such a link for your project page, please display prominently =
near the=20
link notice that <SPAN class=3Demphasis><EM>we are not a help desk for =
your=20
project!</EM></SPAN></P>
<P>We have learned the hard way that without such a notice, we will =
repeatedly=20
be pestered by idiots who think having published this document makes it =
our job=20
to solve all the world's technical problems.</P>
<P>If you're reading this document because you need help, and you walk =
away with=20
the impression you can get it directly from the authors of this =
document, <SPAN=20
class=3Demphasis><EM>you</EM></SPAN> are one of the idiots we are =
talking about.=20
Don't ask <SPAN class=3Demphasis><EM>us</EM></SPAN> questions. We'll =
just ignore=20
you. We are here to show you how to get help from people who actually =
know about=20
the software or hardware you're dealing with, but 99.9% of the time that =
will=20
not be us. Unless you know for <SPAN =
class=3Demphasis><EM>certain</EM></SPAN> that=20
one of the authors is an expert on what you're dealing with, leave us =
alone and=20
everybody will be happier.</P></DIV>
